                  </persName>
               
            .</p>
               <p>Another Count, for stealing, on the 13th day of December last, 4 lb. weight of thread value 9 s. 4 d. and thirty yards of ferret, value 4 s. 6 d. the property of the said John Welsford.</p>
               <p>Another Count, for stealing, on the 15th day of December last, the same goods, and one gross of metal plated buttons, value 4 s. 9 d. the property of the said John Welsford.</p>
               <p>And 
               
                  <persName id="t17880109-40-defend413" type="defendantName">
                     WILLIAM 
                     ANNAND
                  <interp inst="t17880109-40-defend413" type="surname" value="ANNAND"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880109-40-defend413" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880109-40-defend413" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             was indicted for <rs id="t17880109-40-off202" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17880109-40-off202" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880109-40-off202" type="offenceSubcategory" value="receiving"></interp>
               receiving them, knowing them to have been stolen
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>The said 
               <persName id="t17880109-40-person414">
                  John
                   Langford
               <interp inst="t17880109-40-person414" type="surname" value="Langford"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880109-40-person414" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17880109-40-person414" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             was also charged with stealing, on the 18th of December last, six ounces of twist, value 9 s. a gross of metal buttons, value 4 s. 9 d. fourteen ounces of white sewing silk, value 2 s. 6 d. the property of the said 
               <persName id="t17880109-40-person415">
                  John
                   Welsford
               <interp inst="t17880109-40-person415" type="surname" value="Welsford"></interp>
